channel.title: Sylents fun Making music without hearing it challenge!
channel.description: So i was watching some youtube and saw some people do this so i thought WHY NOT MAKE THIS A CHALLANGE ON AUXY.Its pretty simple as the title says make a track that is 0:30-4:00 long and without hearing the track Never.DONT CHEAT.Believe me it will be 10x more fun after all the work you hear your track for the first time.I willl pick top 3.The challenge submissions end on 25th of this week(when the new update releases).Have fun everyone!!!!!!

item.description:
OK, I was wrong about the broadcasting, but right about the spamming.

If you’re going to specifically invite someone, at least try to make some notional reference to them - and maybe why you invited them - in the thread.

Or maybe just post the thread and leave it to them if they want to engage.

Otherwise, it is just spam.

(As mentioned, I actually mute this category.)

 
Edit:

OK, I probably came in a bit hard. Apologies for that.
Still, what you did was effectively spamming.

Anyhoo…
